sentences: Kristine Meredith Flaherty (born June 30, 1985), better known as K. Flay, is an American singer, songwriter, rapper, and musician.
Her debut album Life as a Dog was released in 2014, peaking on the Billboard Heatseekers Albums chart at No. 2 and Billboard's Rap Albums chart at No. 14.
In 2016, she signed with Interscope Records as the first artist signed to Dan Reynolds' Night Street Records imprint.
